# vibe-audit does not currently require any environment variables to run.
# This file is kept as a placeholder / convention so that if configuration
# is ever needed, contributors know where to document it. Never put real
# secrets in .env — it is gitignored, but this .env.example file is committed
# and must only ever contain fake, illustrative values.

# Example of the kind of fake value that belongs here (not currently used):
# VIBE_AUDIT_DEFAULT_TIMEOUT_MS=8000
